original_title: ファルコムjdkバンドディーバ 小寺可南子シングス DVD Video
overview: Falcom jdk's own diva Kanako Kotera takes you along many of the most famous vocal works from Falcom's title library and teaches you how to perfect them for karaoke nights. Her friends in the jdk band come along to provide the music.
title: Falcom Jdk Band Diva Kanako's How to Sing Falcom Songs DVD Video
